                  </hi>. I am single, and live in Long-walk, Bermondsey-square. On Tuesday evening, between five and six o'clock, I was at Greenwich fair with my sister—I felt a hand in my pocket—I turned, and the officer had got the prisoner—I had a shilling, a sixpence, a halfpenny, and a farthing—my money was gone, and his hand was taken as it came out of my pocket—the money fell on the ground.</p>
